Revision history for Class::Tag module:

0.01  March 2013
	- Original prototype (Big Bang) version used internally by early versions of Object::Hybrid 

0.02_01 18 April 2013
	- Complete revision and growing test suit. This is the first version released to CPAN as separate module.
	
0.03 22 April 2013
	- First more or less decent version, with concept articulated more clearly. Many changes. Object::Hybrid now depends on it.
	
0.04 22 April 2013
	- Documentation improvements.
